@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tsdbfz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(0.37)
    tmp = wp.exp((v2 - (v2 + 0.06 + tmp + 0.36)))
    v1 = wp.abs((tmp * (tmp + 0.61 / tmp + 0.01)))
    tmp = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.03 / v0 + 0.97) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.14)))
    data[tid] = v0
